pfSense CIDR Calculator - An interactive IPv4 and IPv6 CIDR subnet calculator for pfSense.

Features:
- Real-time subnet calculations with IPv4 and IPv6 support
- Network address, broadcast, and usable host range calculation
- CIDR notation conversion and wildcard mask generation
- Dashboard widget for quick access
- No server-side processing - all calculations client-side

Accessible via Diagnostics menu and as an optional Dashboard widget.

WWW: https://github.com/IFeelFine/pfSense-pkg-CIDRCalculator